metadata.name: You may experience fear
metadata.description:
In a certain kingdom lived a girl named Lisa. She was a fearless warrior, riding a horse and defending her castle.
She knew how to hammer a nail, make soup, and sew a dress. But here's the trouble. She was afraid to stand on a stool. She was so afraid that she cried every time she had to do it. 
One day she was having fun with her friends. They offered her to drink a potion of courage, and then, brave Lisa wanted to climb a tall telephone tower to conquer her fear. 
All her friends dissuaded her and made her climb down, but she wouldn't listen to them. She climbed higher and higher through the clouds. 
At the very top, a breathtaking view of her small town awaited her. It was a view she had never seen before. 
Lisa was incredibly happy that she had done this. She would never have seen her town from the top if she hadn't been afraid to stand on a stool.
